sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/SDK
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Route as ds-pipeline Route<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS Reencrypt
    participant OAuth as OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS Service CA
    participant APIServer as DS Pipelines API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP
    participant MariaDB as MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP MySQL
    participant Storage as Minio/S3<br/>9000/443 HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Argo as Argo Workflows<br/>K8s API 443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Runner as Pipeline Runner Pods
    participant MLMD as MLMD Envoy<br/>9090/TCP gRPC
    participant MLMDServer as MLMD gRPC Server

    Note over User,MLMDServer: Flow 1: Pipeline Submission

    User->>Router: POST /apis/v2beta1/pipelines<br/>HTTPS/443
    Router->>Route: Forward HTTPS/8443<br/>TLS 1.2+ Reencrypt
    Route->>OAuth: Forward HTTPS/8443<br/>Service CA cert
    OAuth->>OAuth: Validate OAuth2 Bearer Token
    OAuth->>APIServer: Forward HTTP/8888<br/>Delegated auth
    APIServer->>MariaDB: Store pipeline metadata<br/>MySQL/3306<br/>User/Pass auth
    MariaDB-->>APIServer: Confirm
    APIServer->>Storage: Store pipeline artifacts<br/>HTTP(S)/9000 or 443<br/>Access/Secret Key
    Storage-->>APIServer: Confirm
    APIServer-->>OAuth: 200 OK
    OAuth-->>Route: Response
    Route-->>Router: Response
    Router-->>User: Pipeline created

    Note over APIServer,Runner: Flow 2: Pipeline Execution

    APIServer->>Argo: Create Workflow CR<br/>K8s API 443/TCP HTTPS<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Argo->>Runner: Launch pipeline pods<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Runner->>Storage: Download artifacts<br/>HTTP(S)/9000 or 443<br/>Access/Secret Key
    Storage-->>Runner: Artifacts
    Runner->>Runner: Execute pipeline step
    Runner->>Storage: Upload results<br/>HTTP(S)/9000 or 443<br/>Access/Secret Key

    Note over Runner,MLMDServer: Flow 3: ML Metadata Tracking

    Runner->>MLMD: Log metadata<br/>gRPC/9090
    MLMD->>MLMDServer: Forward gRPC
    MLMDServer->>MariaDB: Store ML metadata<br/>MySQL/3306<br/>User/Pass
    MariaDB-->>MLMDServer: Confirm
    MLMDServer-->>MLMD: Response
    MLMD-->>Runner: Metadata logged

    Note over User,APIServer: Flow 4: UI Access

    User->>Router: Access UI<br/>HTTPS/443
    Router->>Route: ds-pipeline-ui Route<br/>HTTPS/8443 Reencrypt
    Route->>OAuth: HTTPS/8443<br/>Service CA cert
    OAuth->>OAuth: Validate OAuth2 Bearer Token
    OAuth->>APIServer: Fetch pipeline data<br/>HTTP/8888<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    APIServer->>MariaDB: Query metadata<br/>MySQL/3306
    MariaDB-->>APIServer: Pipeline data
    APIServer-->>OAuth: Data response
    OAuth-->>User: UI displays pipelines
